---
import ImagePlaceholder from "../components/ImagePlaceholder.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/SectionHeader.astro";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";


---

<Base
  title="Our Programs | iPlay, iDiscover, iLead & ILP | WWIS Trichy"
  description="Explore WWIS programs: iPlay for Pre-KG to Grade 2, iDiscover for Grades 3–7, iLead for Grades 8–12, and Individual Learning Plans."
  pageType="CollectionPage"
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Our Programs"
    title="A complete learning journey from play to leadership"
    text="WWIS offers stage-wise programmes designed to nurture every child through Cambridge standards, purposeful play, project-based learning, and personalized growth."
    primaryLabel="Apply for Admission"
    primaryHref="/find-us#admission-form"
    secondaryLabel="Meet Our Team"
    secondaryHref="/our-team"
  />

  <!-- iPlay -->
  <section class="program-section" id="iplay">
    <div class="program-section__header fade-up">
      <p class="eyebrow">Early Years</p>
      <h2>iPlay – Pre KG to Grade 2</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="program-images fade-up">
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/iplay%20image.jpg" label="[IPLAY IMAGE 1]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/iplay%20image%202.jpeg" label="[IPLAY IMAGE 2]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/iplay%20image%203.jpeg" label="[IPLAY IMAGE 3]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/iplay%20image%204.jpeg" label="[IPLAY IMAGE 4]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="program-content fade-up">
      <blockquote class="program-quote">
        "The first five years have so much to do with how the next 80 turn out."
        <cite>— Bill Gates</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <div class="program-text">
        <p>The first eight years of a child's life are the most important for brain development. Nearly 90% of brain development occurs during this period. Every touch, sound, movement, and learning experience strengthens neural connections.</p>
        <p>The iPlay Programme is a research-backed, neuroscience-informed learning approach designed for children aged 2.5 to 7.5 years (Pre KG to Grade 2). It provides purposeful play, sensory engagement, and nurturing learning environments that support curiosity and exploration.</p>
        <p>Children enjoy independent exploration time where they participate in meaningful activities that stimulate creativity, imagination, and problem-solving.</p>
        <p>A balanced routine including play, rest, quiet activities, and structured learning helps children develop emotional regulation, concentration, confidence, and social skills.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="program-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Learning is supported through</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Multi-sensory activities</li>
            <li>Open learning spaces</li>
            <li>Caring teachers</li>
            <li>Independent exploration</li>
            <li>Brain development strategies</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Key Highlights</h3>
          <ul class="tag-list">
            <li>Strong emphasis on early brain development</li>
            <li>Multi-sensory learning experiences</li>
            <li>Independent exploration</li>
            <li>Open classrooms</li>
            <li>Research-backed teaching methods</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- iDiscover -->
  <section class="program-section soft-band" id="idiscover">
    <div class="program-section__header fade-up">
      <p class="eyebrow">Middle Years</p>
      <h2>iDiscover – Grade 3 to Grade 7</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="program-images fade-up">
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/idiscover%20image.jpg" label="[IDISCOVER IMAGE 1]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/Idiscover%20image%202.png" label="[IDISCOVER IMAGE 2]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/Idiscover%20image%203.jpeg" label="[IDISCOVER IMAGE 3]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/Idiscover%20image%204.png" label="[IDISCOVER IMAGE 4]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="program-content fade-up">
      <div class="program-text">
        <p>The iDiscover Programme is designed for students aged 7.5 to 12.5 years (Grades 3–7). It combines strong academics with real-world learning experiences and helps students discover their unique talents, passions, and strengths.</p>
        <p>Students participate in:</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="tag-list program-tags">
        <li>Project-Based Learning</li>
        <li>Exploration Hours</li>
        <li>Language Hours</li>
        <li>Community Meetings</li>
        <li>Book Reviews</li>
        <li>Seminars</li>
        <li>Industrial Visits</li>
        <li>Field Visits</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="program-text">
        <p>The Individual Learning Plan (ILP) enables students to explore career-focused skills such as programming, culinary arts, visual arts, graphic design, robotics, and many more.</p>
        <p>Students also organize and manage school events independently, developing leadership, teamwork, responsibility, and communication skills.</p>
      </div>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Key Highlights</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li>Personalized learning</li>
          <li>Career exploration</li>
          <li>Project-based learning</li>
          <li>Leadership development</li>
          <li>Real-world exposure</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- iLead -->
  <section class="program-section" id="ilead">
    <div class="program-section__header fade-up">
      <p class="eyebrow">Senior Years</p>
      <h2>iLead – Grade 8 to Grade 12</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="program-images fade-up">
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/ilead%20image.jpg" label="[ILEAD IMAGE 1]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/ilead%20image%202.jpeg" label="[ILEAD IMAGE 2]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/Ilead%20image%203.png" label="[ILEAD IMAGE 3]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/ilead%20image%204.jpg" label="[ILEAD IMAGE 4]" aspectRatio="4 / 3" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="program-content fade-up">
      <div class="program-text">
        <p>The iLead Programme prepares students aged 12.5 to 17.5 years (Grades 8–12) for higher education, career success, and leadership.</p>
        <p>Students receive structured academic guidance while exploring future career opportunities through practical learning experiences.</p>
        <p>The programme focuses on:</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="tag-list program-tags">
        <li>Academic excellence</li>
        <li>Career exploration</li>
        <li>Programming</li>
        <li>Technology</li>
        <li>Internship opportunities</li>
        <li>University preparation</li>
        <li>Workplace visits</li>
        <li>Independent learning</li>
        <li>Critical thinking</li>
        <li>Reading habits</li>
      </ul>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Key Highlights</h3>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li>University readiness</li>
          <li>Programming exposure</li>
          <li>Career planning</li>
          <li>Internship opportunities</li>
          <li>Independent thinking</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ILP -->
  <section class="program-section soft-band" id="ilp">
    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="Personalized Learning"
      title="Individual Learning Plan (ILP)"
      text="The Individual Learning Plan (ILP) allows every student to develop their talents through personalized learning experiences. Students work towards goals that match their strengths and interests while receiving continuous guidance from teachers."
    />
    <div class="ilp-intro fade-up">
      <p>Students explore their interests and talents through Individual Learning Plans that shape meaningful goals, guided practice and joyful progress in each area of strength.</p>
      <ImagePlaceholder src="/images/individual%20learning%20plan%20image.jpeg" label="[ILP Image Placeholder]" aspectRatio="16 / 9" loading="lazy" />
      <a class="button button--primary" href="/ilp-programs">Explore All ILP Programs</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .program-section__header {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .program-section__header h2 {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .program-images {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .program-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .program-quote {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--emerald);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .program-quote cite {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 12px;
    color: var(--gold-text);
  }

  .program-text {
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .program-text p {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .program-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .program-grid ul,
  .ilp-card__content ul {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .program-grid li,
  .ilp-card__content li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--charcoal-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .program-tags {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ilp-intro {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-gold);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
  }

  .button {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-dark) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    color: var(--emerald);
    display: inline-flex;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .button:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.24);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }



  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .program-images {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .program-grid,
    .ilp-card,
    .ilp-card--reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      direction: ltr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .program-images {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
